room_title: Escape room "Airplane Crash" by Colorado Escape in Denver
room_description: You and your team are searching for Flight 666! You got a tip that a unlucky passenger on board was carrying a duffle bag full of money!!! The flight crashed in the jungle and hidden somewhere inside is a fortune! The battery in black box beacon only has an hour before it dies and the plane is lost forever! Find the plane and search the wreckage for the duffle bag full of cash!!!
